  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Date: march 13th 1999, \nTime: 06:00\n\nthe research team at lab kal4an
    was successful in developing gs-4x the ultimate genome sequence for the next
    human evolution. the component was sent for final testing at our meno vil lab.\n\nat
    0900, meno vil reported they received a shipment of nutty butty fat burner pills.
    the delivery guy messed up. \n \ngs-4x was delivered to meno villa owned by Terry
    manning a small-time gym coach.  as per the sources, he consumed gs-4x with his
    protien shake.\n\nat 20:00 terry manning bench pressed 2000 lbs.\nhe found this
    when his friends were hyping him up to lift 100 lbs. since then he lives for
    the hype...\n\nwe have decided to secretly fund the strong man trials this year.
    for testing subject \"encourageman\" has to complete series of 2 challenges.
    if sucessful, subject shall be taken to lab kal4an for mass production of gs-4x.
    if failed this shall be the end of encourageman."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3179854d259ed462a97793c1e58e81ee, type: 2}
