  m_text: "Welcome to the Strong Man Trials!\n\nEncourageMan, the world\u2019s most
    motivational superhero, is about to face impossible challenges. But there\u2019s
    one secret nobody knows\u2026\n\nHis invincibility only works when someone cheers
    for him.\n\nChallenge 1: Survive the Crusher-9000\n\nFor the first trial, encourageman
    has to stop the hydraulic crusher with his brare hands.\n\n<-view the instructions
